{"tid":2196901,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"開心速遞｜驚見政治隱喻　TVB稱會嚴肅了解：不能容忍類似事件","createTime":"2020-09-10T08:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T15:52:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":53,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f5009c4c73be7304eb2704a1fd603cb6adbeda","tid":2196901,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"TVB處境劇《愛．回家之開心速遞》在周三（9日）播出的一集，說到飾演「根叔」的劉丹不滿被「雷公」加租十倍，扮成「租霸」將辦公室倒亂，最後熊家全體人員穿上保護衣、戴住黃色手套幫手收拾這個場面。看似沒有什麼特別焦點畫面出現，但有眼利的網友發現掛在電腦屏幕上的手套弄成疑似「五大訴求、缺一不可」手勢，片段播足14秒，亦造成網友熱話，有網友更表示要罷睇TVB。<br />\n<br />\n今天（10日）TVB官方回應此事件：「已經睇過昨晚播出片段，該場面確實已播咗出街，究竟係有心定係巧合，在公司來講巧合嘅機會比較細，相信係有心人刻意做出破壞情況出嚟，公司會嚴肅了解事件，搵出呢啲故意製造破壞嘅人，無綫絕對不能接受亦不能容忍類似事件發生，由於事件牽涉太多人，要搵出涉事者唔容易，但都係必須去做嘅事。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200910/380736401320316928.png/LAap1Wzu8_mXOxtbkLQphiDZbGacZZEpyK9dCsivXQo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200910%2F380736401320316928.png%2FLAap1Wzu8_mXOxtbkLQphiDZbGacZZEpyK9dCsivXQo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dfc1410a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beed2be17521cfa852d834720dcaa71769eb6fe4","tid":2196901,"uid":23833,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:26:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"203ef4a7e7c217883f94622c3797b6fce8034b91","tid":2196901,"uid":11291,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"抵死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連藍絲都抵制愛回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n植入式廣告呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339f45b183